  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a relentless world of the Wild West where dark creatures roam and every bullet counts. In Western Shadowlands, you'll face off against waves of monstrous enemies, upgrading your revolver and enhancing your firepower as you survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras/591f9aafc45c72aebb7d334a09f9ce15.poster.avif?t=1732355170\" width=514 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras/591f9aafc45c72aebb7d334a09f9ce15.webm?t=1732355170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras/591f9aafc45c72aebb7d334a09f9ce15.mp4?t=1732355170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With each wave, both you and the creatures become stronger, forcing you to strategize and adapt as the danger grows. Unleash devastating attacks, discover powerful new abilities, and see how long you can endure in this rogue-like challenge where the only rule is to survive—or face the shadows.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras/782cfa4b2b8de7ddd0ceba4234c7a1ad.avif?t=1732355170\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras_big/782cfa4b2b8de7ddd0ceba4234c7a1ad.avif?t=1732355170 width=800 height=440 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a relentless world of the Wild West where dark creatures roam and every bullet counts. In Western Shadowlands, you'll face off against waves of monstrous enemies, upgrading your revolver and enhancing your firepower as you survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras/591f9aafc45c72aebb7d334a09f9ce15.poster.avif?t=1732355170\" width=514 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras/591f9aafc45c72aebb7d334a09f9ce15.webm?t=1732355170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras/591f9aafc45c72aebb7d334a09f9ce15.mp4?t=1732355170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With each wave, both you and the creatures become stronger, forcing you to strategize and adapt as the danger grows. Unleash devastating attacks, discover powerful new abilities, and see how long you can endure in this rogue-like challenge where the only rule is to survive—or face the shadows.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras/782cfa4b2b8de7ddd0ceba4234c7a1ad.avif?t=1732355170\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras_big/782cfa4b2b8de7ddd0ceba4234c7a1ad.avif?t=1732355170 width=800 height=440 /></span></p>",
